But now, you're the one falling sick.

438
00:37:47,479 --> 00:37:51,680
As your physician, I have to keep an eye on you.

439
00:37:53,599 --> 00:37:57,320
You keep tabs on everything, huh?

440
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:58,799
Of course.

441
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:01,120
I am not as generous as you think.

442
00:38:01,120 --> 00:38:04,919
So once in a while, I'll air your dirty laundry

443
00:38:04,919 --> 00:38:07,840
so that you know not to mess around with me.

444
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:12,339
The land deed already falls under your name.

445
00:38:12,339 --> 00:38:16,460
What more do you want from me?

