448
00:38:28,860 --> 00:38:34,279
Those few letters are enough to send the Zhous and the Suns into a panic.

449
00:38:34,279 --> 00:38:37,900
You also exposed the shortcomings of the Protected Appointments System.

450
00:38:37,920 --> 00:38:41,700
Shen jumped on the occasion and suggested its abolition.

